headline: AVY Q1 Earnings Call: Tariff Uncertainty Clouds Steady Organic Growth and Margin Performance
summary: Adhesive manufacturing company Avery Dennison (NYSE:AVY) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, but sales were flat year on year at $2.15 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.30 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
